---
import BaseLayout from '../../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---
<BaseLayout title="Forecasting Frameworks — Wychwood Partners" description="Driver-based forecasting and scenario planning for confident decisions.">
  <main class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 py-14">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight">Forecasting frameworks</h1>
    <p class="mt-4 max-w-3xl text-slate-600">
      Driver-based forecasting and scenarios that improve confidence, decision velocity, and alignment across leadership and investors.
    </p>

    <div class="mt-10 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6 md:grid-cols-3">
      <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">What it includes</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li>• Revenue + capacity drivers</li>
          <li>• Pipeline confidence rules</li>
          <li>• Scenario planning</li>
          <li>• Monthly forecast cadence</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">When it’s needed</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li>• “We don’t trust the numbers”</li>
          <li>• Surprises late in the month</li>
          <li>• Weak pipeline visibility</li>
          <li>• Investor pressure</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
      <div class="rounded-2xl border bg-white p-6 shadow-sm">
        <p class="text-sm font-semibold">Outcomes</p>
        <ul class="mt-3 space-y-2 text-sm text-slate-600">
          <li>• Forecast confidence</li>
          <li>• Faster decisions</li>
          <li>• Better resource allocation</li>
          <li>• Clear trade-offs</li>
        </ul>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-12 rounded-2xl border bg-slate-50 p-8">
      <p class="text-lg font-semibold">Want a forecasting reset?</p>
      <p class="mt-2 text-sm text-slate-600">We can usually improve clarity inside 2–4 weeks and build a durable model over 6–8.</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="mt-5 inline-flex rounded-xl bg-slate-900 px-5 py-3 text-sm font-medium text-white hover:bg-slate-800">Book a call</a>
    </div>
  </main>
</BaseLayout>
